@nodes BUGS "Bugs"

    MultiUsage has been fully made in assembler so it can have bug because it's an hard langage where debugging is
  difficult. But, I use MultiUsage all the time and I have see nothing anormal but you can't found bugs on your
  machine configuration so you can send the bugs found to @{"me" LINK AUTEUR}. Please respect this template :
 
